-- Enel Spending $1.2 Billion on Renewables Research, Financial Times Reports
-- Ben Martin
-- 2010-06-22T01:08:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/enel-to-invest-1-billion-euros-in-renewable-energy-research-ft-reports.html

          
          
             Enel SpA  Chief Executive Officer
 Fulvio Conti  said the company is spending 1 billion euros ($1.23
billion) in research into renewables, the Financial Times
reported, citing an interview.  
